snippet.title: Tokyo Underground Killer - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2063090/Tokyo_Underground_Killer/

About Tokyo Underground Killer:
Tokyo Underground Killer is a fast-paced, vibrant trip through the neon and blood drenched nights of a fictive Tokyo somewhere in the future.
Take on the role of the notorious assassin Kobayashi, and use your sword and otherworldly blood skills to take out highly dangerous targets all across Tokyo.

With music by Andrew Hulshult
